column5: For me the flu cure is the toilet lol after a day on that I am good.  Mind you that cure seems way better.  Thanks for sharing Simon glad to see you are getting more fish now.
At least a pleasant temporary cure.

Simon,I tried to PM you about this but was getting error msg,there is also a plowed access road on the north side of Eagle,on Evergreen Rd at the end of Townline Rd. I haven't had the chance to get out there yet,shame on me,this 5 min from wear I hang my hat in the winter months. I have heard they are getting some nice fish.
Yep....plans to go fishing this weekend....cough, congestion and achiness setting in as of last night....only makes me want to get out there MORE
